## QUANTIFIED THRESHOLDS

Use these thresholds for severity decisions. Measure from code (field counts, step counts, tap estimates).

### Step/Tap Benchmarks

| Flow type | Target steps | Flag when | Target taps | Flag when |
|-----------|-------------|-----------|-------------|-----------|
| Login/auth | 2-3 | >4 | 3-5 | >6 |
| Single form submit | 3-5 | >6 | 5-10 | >15 |
| Multi-step wizard | 5-8 | >10 | 10-20 | >30 |
| Admin list+action | 3-4 | >6 | 4-6 | >8 |
| Duplicate from prior | 2-3 | >4 | 3-5 | >6 |
| Daily recurring form (with pre-fill) | 3-4 | >5 | 5-8 | >12 |

### Time Impact Benchmarks

| Pattern | Estimated waste per occurrence | Severity when daily |
|---------|-------------------------------|---------------------|
| No pre-fill on repeated values | 30-60s | MEDIUM |
| No auto-save on wizard (restart risk) | 2-5min | HIGH |
| No offline support on field form | 1-10min (travel to signal) | HIGH |
| Filter/sort reset on navigation | 10-20s | MEDIUM |
| No draft recovery | 2-5min per lost draft | HIGH |
| Manual re-entry of user/equipment data | 15-30s | MEDIUM |
| No template/duplicate flow | 30-90s | MEDIUM |

Multiply by estimated daily frequency to quantify weekly impact in findings.

### Field Count Thresholds

| Form type | Target fields visible per step | Flag when |
|-----------|-------------------------------|-----------|
| Wizard step | 3-6 | >8 visible at once |
| Single-page form | 5-10 | >15 without section grouping |
| Quick action form | 1-3 | >5 |

