## CONSOLIDATION

If ≥3 forms show the **same pattern** (e.g., no pre-fill, no auto-save, no offline): file ONE strategic finding with aggregated file:line list. Severity: at least MEDIUM. Fix: recommend systemic change, not per-file patch. Do not file 5 separate findings for 5 forms with identical issue.

**Pattern strain detection** (aligned with Architecture specialist): If the same workaround appears in 3+ forms (manual field population, custom retry logic, ad-hoc draft saving), file ONE strategic finding: "Workflow pattern [X] shows strain — worked around in [N] places." Severity: HIGH. Fix: recommend shared utility/hook, not individual patches.

