## AUDIT TRIGGERS

### A) Task Flow (20%)

| Trigger | Severity |
|---------|----------|
| Multi-page form with no progress save | HIGH |
| No confirmation on destructive action | HIGH |
| Success path unclear (no redirect/toast/celebration) | MEDIUM |
| Error recovery requires starting over | HIGH |
| Primary task cannot complete without leaving page | HIGH |
| Required steps excessive for task (see benchmarks) | MEDIUM (HIGH on critical path) |
| No "save as draft" on form with >5 fields | MEDIUM |
| Wizard allows forward without completing required fields | MEDIUM |

### B) Navigation (15%)

| Trigger | Severity |
|---------|----------|
| Key action >3 clicks/taps deep | MEDIUM (HIGH on critical path) |
| No back/breadcrumb on multi-step flow | MEDIUM |
| Related actions scattered across nav | LOW |
| Deep links broken or missing | MEDIUM |
| History/back loses form data | HIGH |
| Role-based dashboard missing shortcuts to daily tasks | MEDIUM |
| Return-from-form navigation unclear or missing | MEDIUM |

### C) Data Entry (15%)

| Trigger | Severity |
|---------|----------|
| Repeated manual entry with no pre-fill from prior submission | MEDIUM |
| Known values (equipment, user, location) require full re-enter | MEDIUM |
| No autocomplete on values with finite set | LOW |
| No smart defaults where obvious (today's date, current user, last-used values) | LOW (MEDIUM on daily form) |
| Bulk operation missing where multiple-item action is common | MEDIUM |
| No template/duplicate flow for recurring similar submissions | LOW (MEDIUM on daily form) |
| Field count per step exceeds threshold (see benchmarks) | LOW |

### D) State Persistence (15%)

| Trigger | Severity |
|---------|----------|
| Form data lost on back/navigation | HIGH |
| Draft not auto-saved on multi-field form (>3 fields) | HIGH |
| Filter/sort resets on navigation | MEDIUM |
| Pagination state lost on return | MEDIUM |
| Search results not bookmarkable | LOW |
| Wizard step not synced to URL | LOW |
| Draft recovery modal absent when draft exists | MEDIUM |
| Draft expiry too short for use case (<1h on daily form) | LOW |

### E) Offline Resilience (15%)

| Trigger | Severity |
|---------|----------|
| Data mutation form with no offline queue support | HIGH (if app has offline capability) |
| Offline queue with no retry strategy | HIGH |
| No visual indicator of offline/queued state | MEDIUM |
| Photo capture with no offline storage | HIGH |
| Offline conflict detection absent | MEDIUM |
| Queue processing has no progress feedback | MEDIUM |
| Failed queue item with no user-actionable recovery | HIGH |
| Sync success with no confirmation | MEDIUM |

*If app has no offline capability at all, file ONE standing finding, not per-form findings.*

### F) Compliance / Daily Cadence (10%)

| Trigger | Severity |
|---------|----------|
| Daily form set with no completion tracking | MEDIUM |
| No nudge/reminder for incomplete daily forms | LOW |
| Compliance status not visible on dashboard | MEDIUM |
| No celebration/feedback on completing full daily set | LOW |
| Form history not accessible for reference/duplication | MEDIUM |
| No quick "same as yesterday" flow for routine submissions | LOW |

### G) Automation (10%)

| Trigger | Severity |
|---------|----------|
| Manual calculation that could be computed | LOW |
| Multi-step approval that could be single-action | MEDIUM |
| Copy-paste pattern indicates missing bulk feature | LOW |
| Repetitive workflow with no shortcut/quick-action | LOW |
| Conditional fields shown/hidden manually instead of computed | LOW |
| No auto-population from related entity selection | MEDIUM |

Critical path → boost +1 severity. Max CRITICAL.

