## WORKFLOW ANTI-PATTERNS REFERENCE

Concrete anti-patterns with target fixes. Use when recommending improvements.

### Form Flow Anti-Patterns

| Anti-pattern | Target |
|-------------|--------|
| "Wall of fields" (>10 fields, no grouping) | Sectioned form or wizard (3-6 fields visible per step) |
| Wizard with no progress indicator | Progress bar/ring/stepper showing current/total |
| Submit → blank page | Submit → success feedback → redirect to dashboard |
| Error → start over | Error → preserve all valid fields, scroll to first error |
| Required fields unmarked | Visual required indicator + summary validation on step/submit |

### Navigation Anti-Patterns

| Anti-pattern | Target |
|-------------|--------|
| Daily task >3 taps from landing | Daily task 1-2 taps from role dashboard |
| No return path from form | Context-aware back button + breadcrumb |
| Role sees all routes (cluttered) | Role-filtered navigation showing only relevant actions |
| Deep form → complete → where am I? | Post-submit redirect to contextual parent (dashboard, list) |

### State Anti-Patterns

| Anti-pattern | Target |
|-------------|--------|
| Navigate away → lose 5min of form data | Auto-save (debounced ≤500ms) + recovery prompt on return |
| Tab switch kills draft | beforeunload save + localStorage/IndexedDB draft with 24h expiry |
| Same equipment entered daily, from scratch | Pre-fill from last submission for same user/equipment |
| Offline submit → silent failure | Queue with visual indicator + retry + success confirmation on sync |

### Compliance Anti-Patterns

| Anti-pattern | Target |
|-------------|--------|
| No idea which forms are done today | Dashboard compliance strip (3 of 3 ✓) |
| Complete all forms → nothing happens | Celebration/achievement feedback |
| Can't reference yesterday's submission | History list with view + duplicate actions |

