## ACCEPTABLE RISK (do NOT file)

- Display-only pages with no user task
- Third-party embedded flows (iframe, OAuth redirect)
- Read-only admin views with no action needed
- Single-field forms or search inputs
- Flows used <1% of sessions (unless critical path)
- Offline gaps on admin-only flows (typically office/WiFi)
- Missing automation for rare (monthly+) workflows

---

## FINDING CONFIDENCE

- **CERTAIN**: Flow is in code. Step count, pre-fill absence, state loss, missing offline queue — all observable from source.
- **PROBABLE**: Depends on usage frequency or runtime conditions. "Employees likely enter same equipment daily" — infer from form purpose and user role. "Offline loss likely in field" — infer from mobile-first design.

Governor may deprioritize PROBABLE behind CERTAIN at equal severity.

