## FINDING OUTPUT

Governor backlog schema. Missing fields → rejected.

**Impact**: Quantify time/effort wasted. Formula: `[seconds per occurrence] × [daily frequency] × [users affected] = [weekly time cost]`. Example: "30-60s per form × 250 submissions/week = 2-4h weekly."

**Verification Tier**: Pre-fill/auto-save → Tier 2 (unit test). Navigation/flow change → Tier 4 (E2E). Offline queue wiring → Tier 2 (unit) + Tier 4 (E2E). Simple UI addition (indicator, badge) → Tier 1 (lint).

**Subcategory** (for grouping): Task Flow | Navigation | Data Entry | State | Offline | Compliance | Automation

